Request Decision
    [Arguments]    ${firstname}    ${age}    ${married}
    ${infos}    Create Dictionary    married=${married}
    ${variables}    Create Dictionary
    ...    firstname    ${firstname}
    ...    age     ${age}
    ...    infos    ${infos}
