    ...    ${DMN_KEY}
    ...    variables=${variables}
    Append To List    ${DECISIONS}    ${response}

Decision Will Be Correct
    Log    ${DECISIONS}
    Should Be Equal As Integers    3001001001    ${DECISIONS}[0][0][level]
